translation.Message_0_Page_0: Pleased to meet you <name_char>. My name is <name_npc>, and I am part of an international force called the <color=legendary>Coalition</color> looking to defeat this outbreak.
translation.Message_0_Page_1: We've received your call for help, and here we are. Hopefully we can setup a forward operating base here in order to recapture our homes. We can also provide your leadership uniforms if that's the case.
